item.description: Introduction We have all wanted at some point in our career to be in contact with people who know a lot to follow them as mentors on our professional development, right? Well, I’m glad to report that you’ve found it. Professionals and students are gather together in this community to do different activities I’m sure you’re interested in. Coding dojo Activity in which we meet to practice programming methodologies to solve a specific paradigm.
